00:23:57.620 --> 00:24:00.560
She was writing it
on her lunch break.

00:24:00.560 --> 00:24:01.810
GEORGE TILLMAN: Lunch break.

00:24:01.810 --> 00:24:03.100
Short story, too.

00:24:03.100 --> 00:24:04.725
AMANDLA STENBERG: It
was a short story.

00:24:04.725 --> 00:24:05.224
You know?

00:24:05.224 --> 00:24:08.570
She was someone who was
socially active on the internet,

00:24:08.570 --> 00:24:12.940
